次出嚟問埋佢個名同問佢幾歲先... 祝大家都搵到自己愛的人呀! 加油豬唷 ;)"},{"pid":"ca8495dff7326bc3ea763e2a6bf537a203b6711d","tid":509351,"uid":53121,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"有咩好酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攞老豆老母錢去叫私鐘以為自己好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6e3747a81edb5bc9aef14160f43231c2302b03","tid":509351,"uid":62841,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩好酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攞老豆老母錢去叫私鐘以為自己好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n威過你咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de8dc89e2221c731a8c5e68bdd53e37c4da978a","tid":509351,"uid":17421,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"5a6e3747a81edb5bc9aef14160f43231c2302b03","tid":509351,"uid":62841,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩好酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攞老豆老母錢去叫私鐘以為自己好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n威過你咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"但事實上個肥仔係一個無生產力同社會地位嘅肥仔嚟咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同暴發戶無咩分別喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19796092d9318c929c98c9dc1d87bea66d76aca8","tid":509351,"uid":11694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同佢係fd搭fd識..係facebook傾左一個星期...佢同我講好想做我老婆&shy;呀..咁我地就係facebook